- Sì.


509
00:41:53.596 --> 00:41:55.933
La vuoi questa
roba al cocco?


510
00:41:57.233 --> 00:42:00.201
Ok. Ottimo. Hm...

511
00:42:00.203 --> 00:42:02.105
Grazie.

512
00:42:04.708 --> 00:42:06.974
Oh mio Dio.

513
00:42:06.976 --> 00:42:08.809
Ok.

514
00:42:08.811 --> 00:42:10.746
Ok. Ehi.

515
00:42:10.748 --> 00:42:12.681
- Ciao.
- Ciao.


516
00:42:12.683 --> 00:42:15.317
