00:48:00.596 --> 00:48:02.098
Ok.

617
00:48:03.299 --> 00:48:05.666
Quale sarebbe il problema?

618
00:48:05.668 --> 00:48:08.205
Sto male.

619
00:48:09.239 --> 00:48:10.971
Sì?
